<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c2">(٢٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{إِلَّا بَلَاغًا}</span> ... لَكِنْ أَمْلِكُ أَنْ أُبَلِّغَكُمْ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(٢٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{إِنْ أَدْرِي}</span> ... مَا أَدْرِي.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(٢٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{مَّا تُوعَدُونَ}</span> ... العَذَابُ الَّذِي وُعِدْتُّمْ بِهِ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c2">(٢٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{أَمَدًا}</span> ... مُدَّةً طَوِيلَةً.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c2">(٢٧)</span> ... <span class="c3">{يَسْلُكُ}</span> ... يُرْسِلُ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c2">(٢٧)</span> ... <span class="c3">{رَصَدًا}</span> ... مَلَائِكَةً يَحْفَظُونَهُ، وَيَحْرُسُونَهُ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>